        "TileImage": "$($repository 5c309d9c-a738-4d83-898c-e427e6f67d9a).Image",
        "Description": "Good Afternoon 47. Your target, Kate Switzer, is a con artist in the art world. She specializes in attracting unsuspecting art collectors by selling them near perfect art pieces that are actually fakes. Our client is one of these unsuspecting buyers and they have decided that the law will not be able to help them with this matter. We have intel that Kate is currently on vacation with her boyfriend in Miami to watch the race. Kate has been spotted running around by the marina. \r\rGood Luck 47.",
